parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument cluster illumination can cause the driver to be unable to see important gauges, such as the speedometer, fuel gauge, and engine temperature, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The instrument cluster lights do not come on
and engine temperature gauges are not visible
the dashboard lights flicker or do not come on
the instrument cluster takes a long time to warm up
the instrument cluster only works intermittently.

symptoms: The instrument panel lights do not turn on when the engine is cold

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of seat belts to retract properly can lead to loose or unsecured seat belts, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: seat belts do not fit snugly around the person
